{"tid":1115363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慈父遭起重機砸至分屍 遺4名子女","createTime":"2019-04-19T06:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T12:01:49.000Z","uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3f3f5a8f0ef0fc857d6fca76e1556a2fa8e2b3","tid":1115363,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"美國紐約一名曾於伊拉克和阿富汗執勤的軍人，為了養活妻活兒，選擇從事建築行業。詎料他於上周六（13日）不幸遇上工業意外，身體慘遭起重機一分為二。紐約市短短一周內3人因工業意外喪命，當地建築部門稱會就連串事故展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n34歲的埃切瓦里亞（Gregory Echevarria）當日凌晨3時在濕潤環境下，協助組裝一部7公噸重的起重機。<span style=\"color: red;\">不過該起重機吊臂突然鬆脫，並從高空掉了下來。埃切瓦里亞不幸被壓中，身體當場分成兩截而亡</span>，另有2名工人身受輕傷。 <br />\n<br />\n埃切瓦里亞的兄弟當時亦在工地工作，不過未有目睹至親離開人世一刻。據報，埃切瓦里亞現遺下4名子女。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXrGQEj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXrGQEj.png&h=de8232cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nnigga -1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉事地點正在興建一幢25層樓高的建築物，曾因未能符合安全標準，一度於本月2日停工，至上周一（8日）復工。紐約於上周合共發生3宗致命工業意外，一名工人於上周一被從高處掉下的碎片擊斃。另有一人於上周三（10日）由一幢13層樓高的建築物意外墮地身亡。"},{"pid":"02811998d65eeebc712b4df4faecbfe3321845b6","tid":1115363,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74607c03eb827aaa4ddb1b1402c5c2ce620fc15","tid":1115363,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698ea5de2c44738df00e8843e289ed50493b1071","tid":1115363,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da5ed0c968b1d539d72f802b77e752597928dab1","tid":1115363,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"34歲生4件， 人地窮都生日， 港豬慘到連生都唔敢生"},{"pid":"c8617ce3894ecd25ffd9e748bbb6490466a9a7ae","tid":1115363,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:12:32.000Z","msg":"軍人 = Condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e1d7de544286496f5ff604faed3970094be27f","tid":1115363,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"自己死左但生左4件,力架總人口繼續上升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54c9e5afbd5c95291440385d1d7027cbf91744a","tid":1115363,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"黑人，是旦啦"},{"pid":"186ff6f266a627e7241bd2a77f34a561175a6bfa","tid":1115363,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"死得好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35e1d91de7a3aedbaef3a8e4b44ff61928f8e7e","tid":1115363,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"以為有圖"},{"pid":"21977c8328611aadcc2a39c078540fdb34f957e1","tid":1115363,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"Salute"}]}